<quickviewtext name="Quick View">
<![CDATA[
<p>The Design major is for students who want to deepen their creative, communication, and interpersonal skills while at the same time develop in-depth skills in multiple areas of design. Design is multidisciplinary and collaborative. Students prepare to work with everyone in the room; those doing engineering, coding, manufacturing, or utilizing our designs.</p>
